===Etymology===
Because this goose nests in the far north, Europeans never saw its chicks, and invented a theory that the {{vern|goose barnacle}} is the larval form of the barnacle goose.
[[Image:Branta leucopsis.jpg|thumb|right|A barnacle goose.]]

